data.description: Welcome to 293 Williams Meadow Lane! In the highly sought after Northern Davidson county area, this home gives you a Winston Salem address with a Davidson County tax rate! This 3 bed/2 bath home is situated on almost a full acre. The main level has all 3 bedrooms. Large primary suite with walk in closet and large primary bathroom. Each bedroom is larger than new home builds today! Make sure you check out the bonus room and the attic storage! There is a full unfinished basement that can be finished, plus enough space to park 2 vehicles! Imagine your coffee on the full covered front porch or late summer afternoons in the above ground pool! Don;t miss out on your opportunity in this neighborhood! They don't come around often!
